title: Late Mike Ilitch quietly paid Rosa Parks’ rent for years| Latest News Videos
text:
Late Mike Ilitch quietly paid Rosa Parks’ rent for years Feb. 16, 2017 - 1:34 - Billionaire Mike Ilitch, who was Little Caesars founder and former owner of MLB’s Detroit Tigers and NHL’s Detroit Red Wings, quietly paid Rosa Parks’ rent for many years. Goodwill revelations come days after Ilitch’s death
